I choose: 李俊毅

I choose 李俊毅 because "毅" means "determination" or "perseverance" in Chinese, which suggests that the person is strong-willed and capable of handling challenges. This is a desirable quality in an employee. –  user21820 Mar 26 '17 at 16:46
@user21820 That's a great analysis! I didn't think about the meaning of the character "毅" when I was reading the list. Your choice makes sense. –  klm123 Mar 26 '17 at 17:15
